{"id":25,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":17,"title":"17. Thanksgiving","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":24,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/17-thanksgiving.25/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/17-thanksgiving-2019-03-20-05-37-29/0-17-thanksgiving.mp3","transcript":"We are having Thanksgiving at our house.\nMy whole family is coming.\nMy parents bought a turkey.\nIt weighs 30 pounds.\nIt takes a long time to cook.\nMy mom wakes up early to cook the turkey.\nI clean the house with my dad.\nThe house smells good.\nWe help Mom in the kitchen.\nI peel potatoes and carrots.\nMy dad makes pumpkin pies.\nMy mom cooks squash.\nI help my mom make stuffing.\nI mix the bread and spices.\nWe make good stuffing.\nIt goes inside the turkey.\nWe put on nice clothes.\nI set the table.\nMy dad carves the turkey.\nMy mom makes the gravy.\nOur relatives arrive.\nWe say \"thank you\" for all we have.\nWe eat and eat.\nIt is a good Thanksgiving.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:31","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"We are having Thanksgiving at our house.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/17-thanksgiving-2019-03-20-05-37-29/1.mp3","time_start":2.9,"time_end":5.47},{"position":2,"content":"My whole family is coming.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/17-thanksgiving-2019-03-20-05-37-29/2.mp3","time_start":5.8,"time_end":7.89},{"position":3,"content":"My parents bought a turkey.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/17-thanksgiving-2019-03-20-05-37-29/3.mp3","time_start":8.5,"time_end":10.41},{"position":4,"content":"It weighs 30 pounds.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/17-thanksgiving-2019-03-20-05-37-29/4.mp3","time_start":10.9,"time_end":13.0},{"position":5,"content":"It takes a long time to cook.","audio_url":"https://dailydi